videoDetails.title: Impossible Trackmania Shortcut Finally Done After 13 Years
videoDetails.shortDescription:
Trackmania players are incredibly dedicated, and it's not often that they're willing to disregard something as impossible. But on the track D07-Race there was an absurd shortcut idea that players commonly agreed was far too difficult to be done. But despite the seeming impossibility, a handful of pioneers dedicated themselves to trying it... and now, they finally did the unthinkable. This is the story of D07 Race.

Watch me live on Twitch:
